Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.51,1080CN,,0,0,0,,哈喽呀
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.51,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Hello there
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.51,0:00:05.68,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我叫Gavin，字幕翻译给虫，欢迎观看这期视频，很奇怪吧这期在我家
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.51,0:00:05.68,1080EN,,0,0,0,,My name's Gavin, and welcome to this episode of the Slow Mo Guys very oddly presented from my living room
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.96,0:00:10.48,1080CN,,0,0,0,,之前我做过一个视频叫“相机慢动作下是怎样工作的”，反响不错
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.96,0:00:10.48,1080EN,,0,0,0,,A while ago, I made a video called   "How a camera works in slow-mo" and the response was great
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.66,0:00:15.66,1080CN,,0,0,0,,所以我自然想做一期电视在慢动作下是怎样工作的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.66,0:00:15.66,1080EN,,0,0,0,,so I thought a good natural progression to that video would be how a TV works in slow-mo
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.67,0:00:20.30,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这是一台85寸的LCD电视，无论我用它玩什么
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.67,0:00:20.30,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This is an 85 inch LCD TV and whenever I'm playing something on it
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.61,0:00:26.57,1080CN,,0,0,0,,或者看什么节目，我的眼睛和大脑都被欺骗了，让我以为
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.61,0:00:26.57,1080EN,,0,0,0,,or watching something on it, my eyes and brain are being misled and tricked, giving me the illusion
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.51,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我在看运动的物体，但实际上我看到的是
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.51,1080EN,,0,0,0,,of watching a moving object when in fact I'm just watching
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.76,0:00:33.08,1080CN,,0,0,0,,一连串静止画面，只是显示得非常快
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.76,0:00:33.08,1080EN,,0,0,0,,several still images just shown to me very, very fast
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.08,0:00:37.60,1080CN,,0,0,0,,比如如果我看的是电影，我一秒会看到24张图片
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.08,0:00:37.60,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If I'm watching a film, I'm being shown 24 images every second
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.60,0:00:43.48,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛仿佛在看移动物体，而实际上我每秒在看24张静止画面
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.60,0:00:43.48,1080EN,,0,0,0,,and to my eyes that looks like I'm looking at a moving object, when in fact I'm looking at 24 individual pictures
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.48,0:00:48.62,1080CN,,0,0,0,,如果我在玩游戏，那就是每秒30或者60帧
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.48,0:00:48.62,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If I'm playing a game, it's the same except maybe 30 to 60 frames a second
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.62,0:00:50.46,1080CN,,0,0,0,,如果是在用电脑，帧数可能会上百
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.62,0:00:50.46,1080EN,,0,0,0,,and if I'm on a PC it could be hundreds
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.46,0:00:51.34,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这帮屁吸优越狗
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.46,0:00:51.34,1080EN,,0,0,0,,PC Master Race
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.34,0:00:57.50,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但是电视实际上不能一下子显示一整张图，1/24秒后再显示下一张
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.34,0:00:57.50,1080EN,,0,0,0,,But a TV like this is actually incapable of showing you one image, and then a twenty-fourth of a second later
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.50,0:00:59.88,1080CN,,0,0,0,,但是电视实际上不能一下子显示一整张图，1/24秒后再显示下一张
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.50,0:00:59.88,1080EN,,0,0,0,,just switching all at once to the next image
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.88,0:01:06.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而要演示这点，我要使用老式的CRT显示器
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.88,0:01:06.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And to illustrate this next point, I'm gonna use a very old, and very crap CRT TV
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.34,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这是射频线
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.34,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That stands for cathode ray tube
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.52,1080CN,,0,0,0,,如果你们注意过的话
Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.52,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If you've ever seen one of these filmed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.52,0:01:15.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你们可能发现摄像机里的电视和我们眼睛看到的不太一样
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.52,0:01:15.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,you may notice that it looks slightly different on camera than it does to your eye
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.38,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.38,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.38,0:01:21.84,1080CN,,0,0,0,,会这样闪的原因是这台摄像机快门速度
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.38,0:01:21.84,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The reason it looks like this is because the shutter speed of this camera
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.84,0:01:25.42,1080CN,,0,0,0,,和显示器的刷新速度不同步
Dialogue: 2,0:01:21.84,0:01:25.42,1080EN,,0,0,0,,is out of sync with the refresh rate of this screen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.42,0:01:28.58,1080CN,,0,0,0,,每一帧图像是从上到下形成
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.42,0:01:28.58,1080EN,,0,0,0,,The frame is constructed from the top to the bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.80,0:01:31.92,1080CN,,0,0,0,,每秒很多次——美国这里是60次，即刷新率60Hz
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.80,0:01:31.92,1080EN,,0,0,0,,multiple times per second -- that's 60 times in the US, 60 Hertz
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.96,0:01:36.42,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我很久以前已经用V2511高速摄像机准备好一些片段
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.96,0:01:36.42,1080EN,,0,0,0,,I've prepared for you some high-speed footage that I shot a long time ago on the V2511
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.92,1080CN,,0,0,0,,其中包含这个CRT显示器，和后面这个LCD，还有些其他的
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.92,1080EN,,0,0,0,,of this screen and this screen and some others
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.18,0:01:43.98,1080CN,,0,0,0,,当中不少是Dan在NES上玩超级玛丽的菜鸡录像
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.18,0:01:43.98,1080EN,,0,0,0,,A lot of it is Dan playing Super Mario on the NES extremely badly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.20,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这里是电视和喵星人在每秒25帧下的画面
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.20,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Here's the TV and the cat played back at 25
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.00,1080CN,,0,0,0,,视频里的速度和实际时间是一样的
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.00,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This is how it would be perceived in real time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.68,1080CN,,0,0,0,,然后是每秒1600帧，你能清楚看到扫描线从上到下在扫描
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.68,1080EN,,0,0,0,,and now at 1600 frames a second you can actually see the scan line moving from the top to the bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.68,0:01:58.84,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你能注意到在CRT显示器里，只有一横条像素会亮
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.68,0:01:58.84,1080EN,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that on a CRT screen, it's only the active line of pixels that's bright
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.36,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而视觉暂留会让你看到一幅完整画面
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.36,1080EN,,0,0,0,,and your persistence of vision will actually build that into a complete image
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.16,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我特么快被晃瞎了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.16,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It's messing with my eyes this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.70,1080CN,,0,0,0,,跟迪厅似的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.70,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It's like a dance floor
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.20,1080CN,,0,0,0,,哎呦我去我这第一个怪都没跳过去
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.20,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Aghhh... Didn't even make it past the first guy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.84,1080CN,,0,0,0,,接下来放慢到每秒2500帧
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.84,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Slowed all the way down to 2500 frames a second
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.86,0:02:27.30,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你现在能看清每一帧是从上到下形成的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.86,0:02:27.30,1080EN,,0,0,0,,you can now differentiate each individual frame being built from top to bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.94,0:02:38.12,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这需要非常高速的摄像机才能看清这个“从上到下”的过程
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.94,0:02:38.12,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It takes an extremely fast camera to see that each frame is built line by line from top to bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.46,0:02:45.06,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而想要看清每一横条从左到右的形成，则需要更更更高速的摄像机
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.46,0:02:45.06,1080EN,,0,0,0,,but it takes an even faster camera to see that each line is drawn from left to right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.18,0:02:51.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,放慢到每秒28500帧，我们勉强能感觉到这个“从左到右”的过程，但这还不够
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.18,0:02:51.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Slow down to 28,500 frames a second we're now seeing glimpses of that, but we do need to go even slower
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.70,1080CN,,0,0,0,,现在减慢到118000帧每秒
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.86,0:02:55.70,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This is now 118,000 frames a second
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.07,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我把数据放上面供你们参考
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.07,1080EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put the stats up for you here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.78,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你可以看到对应的实际时间，也能看清一条线是怎样
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.78,1080EN,,0,0,0,,so you can see the actual amount of time that it took, and you can see now that the line is being drawn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.95,1080CN,,0,0,0,,从左到右画过去的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.95,1080EN,,0,0,0,,from left to right on the screen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.54,1080CN,,0,0,0,,现在是每秒146000帧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.98,0:03:07.54,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Now a 146,000 frames a second
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.10,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你们感受下现在有多慢了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.10,1080EN,,0,0,0,,To gain perspective on just how slow this actually is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.94,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你们看下面这时间
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.94,1080EN,,0,0,0,,You can see the exact time I shot this.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.94,0:03:17.62,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这是小时，刚过午夜，0点23分41秒
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.94,0:03:17.62,1080EN,,0,0,0,,So this is hours, it was just past midnight, 23 minutes 41 seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.62,0:03:24.28,1080CN,,0,0,0,,然后是十分之一秒，百分之一秒，千分之一秒，也就是一毫秒，然后接下来
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.62,0:03:24.28,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This is a tenth of a second, a hundredth of a second, one thousandth of a second or a millisecond, and then over here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.34,1080CN,,0,0,0,,是万分之一秒
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.34,1080EN,,0,0,0,,you've got a ten thousandth of a second
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.46,0:03:32.76,1080CN,,0,0,0,,然后十万分之一秒，然后百万分之一秒，也就是一微秒
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.46,0:03:32.76,1080EN,,0,0,0,,A hundred thousandth of a second, and this unit here is the millionth of a second or a microsecond
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.76,0:03:37.88,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们现在是每秒38万帧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.76,0:03:37.88,1080EN,,0,0,0,,We are now at 380,000 frames a second as our recording frame rate
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.88,0:03:42.70,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这是迄今为止本频道用到的最高的帧数了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.88,0:03:42.70,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That is the highest frame rate we've ever shot so far on this channel and using this information
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.70,0:03:52.98,1080CN,,0,0,0,,于是你们能发现，CRT显示器能在38万分之一秒内画完马里奥大叔的胡子
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.70,0:03:52.98,1080EN,,0,0,0,,here's a little bonus fact: a CRT screen can draw Mario's moustache in less than a 380,000th of a second
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.08,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你说这胡子长的多快
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.08,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That is some seriously fast facial hair
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.58,0:04:01.48,1080CN,,0,0,0,,如果你奇怪为啥画面这么模糊，那是因为这显示器分辨率只有
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.58,0:04:01.48,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And if you're wondering why this footage looks extremely mucky and blurry, it's because the resolution is only
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.48,0:04:05.72,1080CN,,0,0,0,,256x128，如果放到4k画面里，它只有……
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.48,0:04:05.72,1080EN,,0,0,0,,256 by 128 which plunked into a 4k frame is...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.58,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这么大
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.58,1080EN,,0,0,0,,this big
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.58,0:04:13.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,之前那是标准的CRT分辨率（此处存疑），这是4k显示器，即
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.58,0:04:13.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That CRT screen is standard def. This is a 4k screen which means it's
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.40,0:04:21.44,1080CN,,0,0,0,,3840x2160像素，超过八百万像素。所以你们想想这个点是处理图像的能力
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.40,0:04:21.44,1080EN,,0,0,0,,3840 by 2160 pixels that's over 8 million pixels. So think of the processing power that this TV
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.37,1080CN,,0,0,0,,要求它更新一幅那么大的画面
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.37,1080EN,,0,0,0,,has to have to update an image
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.37,0:04:29.92,1080CN,,0,0,0,,每秒还要更新那么多次。首先你会注意到现代LCD显示器
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.37,0:04:29.92,1080EN,,0,0,0,,that big for that many times every second. The first thing you'll notice about a modern LCD screen is that it's
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.78,1080CN,,0,0,0,,不是只点亮某一横条的像素
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.78,1080EN,,0,0,0,,not only the active line of pixels that retains brightness
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.78,0:04:38.08,1080CN,,0,0,0,,它会保持整个图像全亮，所以实际上在扫描线从上往下走时你能看到整幅图像
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.78,0:04:38.08,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It's the entire image, so you can actually see the full image as each scanline passes down the screen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.08,0:04:42.32,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这是Xbox One开启启动画面
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.08,0:04:42.32,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This is every frame of the startup sequence on an Xbox One
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.84,0:04:55.40,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我还录了一段我玩光环的视频，不是想让你知道慢动作下自己瞄准有多菜
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.84,0:04:55.40,1080EN,,0,0,0,,I also recorded myself playing game of Halo nothing to make you feel worse about your performance
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.40,0:04:58.45,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我还录了一段我玩光环的视频，不是想让你知道慢动作下自己有多菜
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.40,0:04:58.45,1080EN,,0,0,0,,than watching your lousy aim in slow-mo look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.47,1080CN,,0,0,0,,其实想想你在玩游戏的时候，电视实际上是这样工作的还是挺有意思的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.47,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It's crazy to think that when you're playing Halo. This is actually what is happening on your TV
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.92,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你要是能看这么快的话，你就有可能打过五五开了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.92,1080EN,,0,0,0,,If only you could see it as speed your aim would be incredible
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.78,1080CN,,0,0,0,,所以讲真我有时候看电视看睡着了，感觉真的好伤心
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.78,1080EN,,0,0,0,,It honestly makes me feel bad when I fall asleep watching TV
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.78,0:05:15.73,1080CN,,0,0,0,,电视君那边忙得不行每秒刷新上千万像素点
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.78,0:05:15.73,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Knowing that this TV is doing all this intensive work changing literally tens of millions of pixels
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.77,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而你却在睡大觉不看它
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.77,1080EN,,0,0,0,,every second and there's no one there watching it
