Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.79,1080EN,,0,0,0,,so if you're watching a video in landscape mode on your iPhone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.84,0:05:32.47,1080CN,,0,0,0,,你的画面其实是从左往右或者从右往左刷新的，取决于你怎么转的手机
