Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.50,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这刚好印证了肉眼是看不到刷新方向的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.50,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That just proved to me that you can't see the Refresh direction with your naked eye
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.50,1080CN,,0,0,0,,因为我完全不知道每次我用iPhone看B站视频的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.50,0:05:40.50,1080EN,,0,0,0,,because I had no idea whenever I was watching a YouTube video on my iPhone that the screen
