Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.98,1080EN,,0,0,0,,was updating in a completely different direction. I'm not sure if this is the case for all smart phones
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.06,0:05:48.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我不确定所有智能手机都这样，但至少这个视频里我的iPhone 7 plus是这样的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.06,0:05:48.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,but it's certainly the case on an iPhone 7 plus which is what I film this on
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.02,0:05:52.28,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们我们刚说了电视的运动图像的显示方法，接下来是
