Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.28,0:05:57.61,1080EN,,0,0,0,,I want to talk about is the illusion of color for this next part. I'm going to need a second camera. Here's one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.90,0:06:03.88,1080CN,,0,0,0,,就你了，哈喽啊，所以想要贴近了看电视，我得把相机焦距
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.90,0:06:03.88,1080EN,,0,0,0,,That's you hello you so in order to film this screen extremely close. I want to set my focus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.20,1080CN,,0,0,0,,调到最近的距离
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.20,1080EN,,0,0,0,,the minimum possible distance
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.20,0:06:12.47,1080CN,,0,0,0,,差不多这里了。当我慢慢向前靠近屏幕的时候，图像越来越清晰
