Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.76,0:06:24.09,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而这是相机想要解析屏幕表面每一个像素点造成的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.76,0:06:24.09,1080EN,,0,0,0,,And what you're seeing there is an effect caused by the camera this camera trying to resolve
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.82,1080CN,,0,0,0,,而这是相机想要解析屏幕表面每一个像素点造成的
