Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.36,0:07:26.24,1080EN,,0,0,0,,Well this close it's a different story altogether, I'm gonna get a tripod. Here's one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.87,1080CN,,0,0,0,,真累啊这活
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.87,1080EN,,0,0,0,,What a mission this is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.90,0:07:36.16,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们现在已经近到往镜头上吹气都能让画面产生明显晃动了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.90,0:07:36.16,1080EN,,0,0,0,,We're so close up right now that I can actually disturb this image by blowing on the lens
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.87,0:07:44.02,1080CN,,0,0,0,,我们能看到子像素点了，每个像素有三个子像素
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.87,0:07:44.02,1080EN,,0,0,0,,We're now looking at the sub pixel level a pixel is made up of three sub pixels
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.65,1080CN,,0,0,0,,红绿蓝，就是RGB，你们以前可能听过
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.65,1080EN,,0,0,0,,red green and blue RGB you may have heard that before and
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.41,0:07:55.54,1080CN,,0,0,0,,通过不同程度的点亮不同子像素来显示不同颜色
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.41,0:07:55.54,1080EN,,0,0,0,,This creates the illusion of different colors by dimming and brightening different sub pixels to different intensities
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.77,0:08:01.00,1080CN,,0,0,0,,这个屏幕能显示上百万种颜色。
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.77,0:08:01.00,1080EN,,0,0,0,,this screen can create the illusion of literally millions of different colors
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.12,1080CN,,0,0,0,,三个都亮时显示白色
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.12,1080EN,,0,0,0,,When all three are lit to full brightness you get white
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.25,0:08:09.85,1080CN,,0,0,0,,三个都变暗时图像就慢慢变灰直到变黑。所以当绿色变暗，红色蓝色变亮
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.25,0:08:09.85,1080EN,,0,0,0,,When all three dim you go through gray all the way down to black so if green dims away and red and blue are still
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.86,0:08:16.46,1080CN,,0,0,0,,就会得到品色。这就是颜色的产生。所以每次你看电视
Dialogue: 2,0:08:09.86,0:08:16.46,1080EN,,0,0,0,,lit then you go into magenta purple. That's all very and that's how the colors are made so every time on your TV
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.68,0:08:23.23,1080CN,,0,0,0,,当你看到白色图像，你看的是无数红色、绿色、蓝色的小灯
